title: Spray-On Bed Liner
description:
Dee Zee Spray Liner allows you to protect a variety of surfaces - just point and spray. Roughly 8 spray cans can coat a standard truck bed. Creates a textured, non-skid surface at half the price of traditional spray liners. For sale within the United States only (not labeled for export).
Part #: DZ97908
